OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,FAn artist has created a unique mural
OL,7,Fto celebrate the National Eisteddfod
OL,8,Fheading to Pontypridd.
OL,10,FThe last time the National Eisteddfod
OL,11,Fcame to Rhondda Cynon Taf was in 1893.
OL,13,FArtist Tom Llewelyn, known as
OL,14,FTee2Sugars, was commissioned by the
OL,15,FEisteddfod to create the piece to
OL,16,Fcelebrate the occasion.
