OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,FThe inspiration behind this is four
OL,7,Fpoems which were written and
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the Eisteddfod, all of
OL,9,Fwhich are based on the national
OL,10,Fanthem, Hen Wlad Fy Nhadau.
OL,12,FThe mural is part of a project which
OL,13,Fhas been created by the National
OL,14,FEisteddfod.
OL,16,FRhondda Cynon Taf was the home of the
OL,17,Fanthem's composers, the father and
OL,18,Fson, Evan and James James. The mural
OL,19,Fis on the wall of their old home on
OL,20,FMill Street, in Pontypridd.
