OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,FTom said the opportunity to create the
OL,7,Fmural has been like "painting on a
OL,8,Fstage in front of thousands and
OL,9,Fthousands of people".
OL,11,FWhile the mural shows an older man and
OL,12,Fhis daughter, he revealed that it is
OL,13,Fbased on a photo he took of his own
OL,14,Fwife and daughter, which he edited for
OL,15,Fthe final painting.
