OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,FAs well as showing the different
OL,7,Fgenerations, Tee2Sugars also explained
OL,8,Fthat the mural is "all about the
OL,9,Fpeople of the Rhondda and Pontypridd
OL,10,Fbeing entwined with the landscape and
OL,11,Fthe River Taff, which is at the centre
OL,12,Fof the piece." As well as the River
OL,13,FTaff, iconic local landmarks such as
OL,14,FCastell Coch and the Rhondda Heritage
OL,15,FPark also occupy part of the mural,
OL,16,Falongside famous Welsh symbols of the
OL,17,Fdaffodil and dragon.
