OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,F"It represents the people and the
OL,7,Flandscape. It's probably the Welshest
OL,8,Fmural I've done in a long time," he
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,FA soundscape has also been created to
OL,12,Faccompany the mural, which was created
OL,13,Fby Screentales from Treherbert,
OL,14,Fcapturing conversations with children
OL,15,Ffrom primary schools in the
OL,16,FEisteddfod's catchment area.
