OL,6,FThese conversations will be heard
OL,7,Finterwoven with various musical
OL,8,Frenditions of the anthem by
OL,9,Findividuals and local choirs in the
OL,10,Fform of a special soundscape.
OL,12,FGeraint James, a descendant of the
OL,13,FJamesses, is heard on the soundscape
OL,14,Fsaying that the anthem words are
OL,15,Fbelieved to have been created as a
OL,16,Fresponse to a letter from two of
OL,17,FEvan's brothers who encouraged members
OL,18,Fof the family to leave Wales and
OL,19,Femigrate to the United States.
