OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,FTo hear the soundscape, you will be
OL,7,Fable to scan the QR code which is on
OL,8,Fthe mural itself to hear it on your
OL,9,Fmobile phone.
OL,11,FAt 7.30pm on Saturday, 10 August,
OL,12,Fthere will be an opportunity to hear
OL,13,Fthe soundscape in the pavilion on the
OL,14,FEisteddfod site, followed by a
OL,15,Fperformance of a new musical
OL,16,Fcommission, 'Gwlad' by Eilir Owen
OL,17,FGriffiths.
