OL,3,CStunning mural created in Pontypridd
OL,4,Cto celebrate Eisteddfod heading to town
OL,6,FThe words of 'Gwlad' are a combination
OL,7,Fof poems written by local poets, Mari
OL,8,FGeorge, Christine James, Delwyn Sion
OL,9,Fand Aneurin Karadog. The piece will be
OL,10,Fperformed by a vocal ensemble of
OL,11,Fformer Eisteddfod winners, as well as
OL,12,Fa chamber orchestra of musicians from
OL,13,FSinfonia Cymru and the National Youth
OL,14,FOrchestra of Wales.
OL,16,FThe soundscape is also available to
OL,17,Flisten on the Eisteddfod's YouTube
OL,18,Fchannel.
